      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-age-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cod-age-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore zero                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-cod-age           not  = zero
                     go to acc-cod-age-600.
